{"tid":675678,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劫太子珠寶】天眼大曝光 兩匪27秒掠500萬珠寶","createTime":"2018-05-23T17:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T02:28:08.000Z","uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6497c7b9dfc1a8d61e24b4ad603b4169c8e128fe","tid":675678,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"【劫太子珠寶】天眼大曝光 兩匪27秒掠500萬珠寶 <br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴海港城太子珠寶遇劫案，《蘋果》獲得一條店舖的閉路電視錄影，拍下匪徒的犯案經過。由片段可見，兩名分別戴白色帽及紅色帽的男子進入店內近門口位置，紅帽男負責掩護，白帽匪徒則迅速用硬物撬飾櫃，不足10秒將玻璃撬爆棄於地上，並大肆搜掠，他12秒內將多件首飾放入斜孭袋內。其間店內顧客及職員發現，紅帽匪徒即取出一把利器揮舞指嚇。兩人得手後急步逃離現場，整個過程僅27秒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58229920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58229920&d=3Ib%2FLvzjMPqzHUsSTPQIOIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=51478a02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F58229920&h=5bb2d468\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180524/58229920</a><br />\n0:18有條友想衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827e5dcb136e32f33103c51d059e4d9bfe94f5f6","tid":675678,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:28:49.000Z","msg":"咁先500萬"},{"pid":"345bb16f24fc732cb2c8797d65a85a66db1dcac9","tid":675678,"uid":167708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"9620aaa23d454e0e6b23f3600f2ffcc8bf34f22a","tid":675678,"uid":52459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:00:03.000Z","msg":"德仔老豆呢？"},{"pid":"446ce50a9ff7223bfff34899b9eec35ba1c5caff","tid":675678,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"商場都搶到"},{"pid":"6f8464677b07ec49deb172b3402be3d8dc6e040c","tid":675678,"uid":55924,"like":0,